<html><head><meta charset="UTF-8"><link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="css/tips.css"></head><body><p><b>Extract Variable refactoring</b></p><p>The <span class="control">Extract Variable</span> refactoring wraps the selected expression into a variable. It adds a new variable declaration and uses the expression as an initializer. Select an expression and press <span class="shortcut">&shortcut:IntroduceVariable;</span> (<span class="control">Refactor | Extract/Introduce | Variable</span>).</p><p class="image"><img src="images/ij_tips_extractvariable.png" alt="extract variable" style="border: 1px solid #55555;" /></p></body></html>